    "5 For a typical 10-year g and r LSST WFD light curve-with ∼ 60 g-band observations and ∼ 170 rband observations (Ivezić et al. 2019)-EzTaoX achieves a reduction in computation time of ∼ 30× over JAVELIN.",
    "When light curves in all six bands are jointly modeled (assuming a total of 800 observations), the performance gain further increases to ∼ 100×.",
    "For a typical 10-year g and r LSST DDF light curve, which contains at least 10 times more observations in both the g and r bands, EzTaoX achieves a speed increase exceeding 2000×.",
